data.description: Sellers will contribute $6,500 towards buyers  closing costs or rate buy down ! This open concept split floorplan, 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home on a generous 0.52 acre corner lot. As you enter the home, you are greeted by a long foyer that guides you to the kitchen, dining area, and living room, designed to entertain guests. The kitchen offers white shaker style cabinets, stainless steel appliances (smooth top stove, microwave, dishwasher, and refrigerator), kitchen island with counter height seating, and corner pantry. The dining area can easily accommodate a large table and chairs. The living room offers plenty of windows for lots of natural light and easily fit a large sectional. Just off the common areas, is a door to the covered back porch overlooking the beautiful backyard. The large master bedroom is located just off the living room and has two windows facing the back yard. The master bathroom has a double vanity, TWO master closets, linen closet, shower, and water closet. Bedrooms 2, 3, and 4 are located off the main foyer hallway at the front of the home. The home also offers and indoor laundry room and two car garage with auto opener. The beautiful 0.52 acre corner lot has lot of grass and trees for privacy and out door enjoyment. Perhaps one of the best extras on this home is the county taxes, Chelco power, Auburn water, and no HOA! Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this home your very own. Schedule your showing today!
